{"tid":576053,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人成日都頭痛？","createTime":"2018-02-28T14:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T12:16:50.000Z","uid":151872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f49f097ad8c4c9c411b521649ab331fdd86e08bd","tid":576053,"uid":151872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:55:55.000Z","msg":"近半年我老豆成日格一排就頭痛<br />\n呢幾次仲痛到嘔 真係嘔番曬d野出黎果隻<br />\n跟住每次都要call白車入院打針先好d<br />\n一般會痛10幾個鐘<br />\n第一次入院照左腦 冇事<br />\n第二次入院 照埋其他耳鼻喉 又冇事<br />\n今次又痛到入左院 但d醫生又係話冇事<br />\n話可能心理作用<br />\n我媽又膽心到工都冇返<br />\n好想知咩事 問親醫生都話冇事<br />\n有冇巴絲都成日頭痛 可以傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9835388698811de2ac0b682711d7b18615d1e1c","tid":576053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a79f77d0f56b25193b14634afe0e605df972d8f","tid":576053,"uid":151872,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9835388698811de2ac0b682711d7b18615d1e1c","tid":576053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩照埋右腦 都係冇事<br />\n咁肥絲知唔知咩事？"},{"pid":"b416429acc19af9909bb0bfae6c0a935e50da8d0","tid":576053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4fb63f217858e6b51ca6c79114cb11275157452","tid":576053,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"應該係偏頭痛？<br />\n一般攰或者感冒頭痛通常瞓一覺就無事，偏頭痛就冇用，一痛痛好耐同埋要食止痛先好d<br />\n我都有頭痛問題，又係照過腦冇事，但冇試過嚴重到真係嘔<br />\n睇醫生都係話偏頭痛醫唔好，唯有開d勁嘅止痛藥<br />\n建議戒煙酒同埋作息健康d囉，有醫生同我講過食煙嘅中年男人好易偏頭痛"},{"pid":"8c433e2c3e5d9ae860fdef1048bbe0fabf1432bc","tid":576053,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會係頸骨有事？果啲位都會導致頭痛"},{"pid":"d789836c728104bee841742fc0843c095822626d","tid":576053,"uid":151872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4fb63f217858e6b51ca6c79114cb11275157452","tid":576053,"uid":173797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:06:27.000Z","msg":"應該係偏頭痛？<br />\n一般攰或者感冒頭痛通常瞓一覺就無事，偏頭痛就冇用，一痛痛好耐同埋要食止痛先好d<br />\n我都有頭痛問題，又係照過腦冇事，但冇試過嚴重到真係嘔<br />\n睇醫生都係話偏頭痛醫唔好，唯有開d勁嘅止痛藥<br />\n建議戒煙酒同埋作息健康d囉，有醫生同我講過食煙嘅中年男人好易偏頭痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:27:48.000Z","msg":"醫生有話過可能係偏頭痛<br />\n但應該唔會咁嚴重 <br />\n因為我姑媽都有偏頭痛 通常食止痛藥就得<br />\n但爸食極止痛藥都冇用<br />\n同埋佢都係早睡早起 唔煙唔酒"},{"pid":"f6fd0646025140ad308c86e62dc688d315cb65b4","tid":576053,"uid":151872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c433e2c3e5d9ae860fdef1048bbe0fabf1432bc","tid":576053,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:09:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會係頸骨有事？果啲位都會導致頭痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:28:30.000Z","msg":"應該冇事 因為佢返工唔洗做搬搬抬抬"},{"pid":"213e302dfd1d468ca2fff1ae35a8a52052ef8525","tid":576053,"uid":151872,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b416429acc19af9909bb0bfae6c0a935e50da8d0","tid":576053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"3a79f77d0f56b25193b14634afe0e605df972d8f","tid":576053,"uid":151872,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9835388698811de2ac0b682711d7b18615d1e1c","tid":576053,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"岩岩照埋右腦 都係冇事<br />\n咁肥絲知唔知咩事？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱啱啱啱啱啱啱啱啱 改左十次"},{"pid":"2eda7c3dc10d61a93fa6c9da0c3273972da98f2d","tid":576053,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/culture/culture_content.asp?contid=8636&amp;srctype=g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fculture%2Fculture_content.asp%3F